{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_25","type":"agent_message","text":"The preserved branch already contains generated metadata and many tests. What remains is not a scaffold problem: the native suite still breaks on reload4j socket deserialization, and the metadata-fix loop kept surfacing new JDK serialization requirements. I’m extracting the last concrete missing-registration evidence from the repair log now."}}
